Cam::

She smiled up at Windlord. She finished the sweets and giggled.  She 
walked up to him and hugged his leg.  Smiling and looking up at 
him, "You wanna play games now?"  She jumped back and transformed 
into fox mode.  She started darting and jumping about. "I wanna play."
